::KitKat::

She walked out of her room with a big smile on her face and humming.  
She walked into the main room and went to the main console.  She 
watched the monitors and checked for maximal activity.  They appeared 
to have left thier area.  She looked up Megatron. "Any orders 
comander?"

She was still mulling the idea of taking the ship in hte back of her 
mind.
